```plantuml
@startuml alfredcs_immersion_day_labs

actor User

box "AWS Services" #LightBlue
    participant S3
    participant SageMaker
    participant FeatureStore
    participant IAM
end box

box "Hugging Face" #LightYellow
    participant "Model Hub" as ModelHub
    participant "Transformers" as Transformers
end box

User -> S3: Upload Dataset
User -> SageMaker: Initiate Model Training
SageMaker -> Transformers: Load Pre-trained Model
Transformers -> SageMaker: Return Model

User -> SageMaker: Fine-tune Model
SageMaker -> ModelHub: Pull Tokenizer
ModelHub -> SageMaker: Return Tokenizer
SageMaker -> SageMaker: Train and Optimize Model

User -> SageMaker: Deploy Model for Inference
SageMaker -> SageMaker: Set up Inference Endpoint

User -> SageMaker: Perform Real-time Inference
SageMaker -> FeatureStore: Retrieve Features
FeatureStore -> SageMaker: Return Features
SageMaker -> User: Return Inference Results

User -> IAM: Set Access Control
IAM -> SageMaker: Apply Policies

@enduml
```